sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User (Browser)
  participant F as Flask Controller (/disease-predict)
  participant P as predict_image()
  participant C as ResNet9 (PyTorch)
  participant DD as disease_dic

  U->>F: POST image file
  F->>P: Preprocess (Resize, ToTensor)
  P->>C: Forward pass
  C-->>P: class index
  P-->>F: class label
  F->>DD: Map to description
  DD-->>F: Advisory content
  F-->>U: disease-result.html

